{
  "stem": "2946.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to hand in our radios.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not allowed to leave-- to be on the street-- I guess after 8 o'clock or after darkness.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to put our Star of David on our clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not allowed to ride-- to be in a-- in a bus or streetcar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were restrictions and restrictions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's about all I can tell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Deportations had started and always 1,000 people were taken to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I bet pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I don't know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people were summoned on a 24-hour basis, and they had to come to Veletrzni Palac.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a something like we had here where they display merchandise, big halls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in one of these halls, there were-- there was a-- by-- by chalk or by paint, a mark 3 by 6 feet-- a square, so to speak-- and there was a number on it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was my number, 558, and as soon as I stepped in-- into the place, they gave me-- [BACKROUND NOISE] they gave me a-- a-- a string on my neck, and on it was a badge, and it says, AM.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the name of the transport-- every transport had a different name or a letter, starting by A, and then AA, AB, and AM.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was AM.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 558 was on this badge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I walked in, and there I see-- on that 3 by 6-- I see this is my place, and it says 558.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I put my little suitcase there, and this is where I'm going to sleep overnight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, they put us in the train and took us 50 kilometers away from Prague was Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
